headline: Wells Fargo to Announce Fourth Quarter 2025 Earnings on Jan. 14, 2026
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, January 07, 2026--Wells Fargo & Company (NYSE: WFC), as previously announced, will report its fourth quarter 2025 earnings results on Wednesday, Jan. 14, 2026, at approximately 7:00 a.m. Eastern time. The results will be available online at https://www.wellsfargo.com/about/investor-relations/quarterly-earnings/.
